{"tid":1942603,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"見到咁多黃絲幫襯藍店真係好欣慰","createTime":"2020-03-25T07:30:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T09:30:03.000Z","uid":132888,"like":21,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"74722dafddd25effc122da811813252b805d6dc0","tid":1942603,"uid":132888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T07:30:33.000Z","msg":"sorry 做左標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母 筲箕灣東大街間藍店Andy&rsquo; bakery 次次出爐前就一堆人排哂長龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />排到去food wise<br />\n相信東大街巴絲會知我講邊度<br />\n仲要串到係行人路掛個龍頭龍尾牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係好撚燥底<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明d蛋糕就又貴又普通又唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申未出和你eat之前我唔知佢係藍店所以食過<br />\n但之後已經無再食<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一條垃圾蛋糕就賣60幾70蚊<br />\n講真 自己係屋企用電飯煲都整到嘅quality<br />\n點解要出去大排長龍幫襯藍店<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最撚嬲嘅係 琴日仲要見到有兩個後生女拎住<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黃店茶色生香</span></span><br />\n嘅飲品係度排隊等出爐<br />\n咁到底你係黃定藍定係港豬啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就係因為你地 依加供到間垃圾藍店係大圍開分店<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咪撚再幫襯藍店啊</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請每次食飯前都善用和你eat FC下啦唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n附上和你eat cap圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ARg45xr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FARg45xr.jpg&h=0f732320&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"54316498a2a3d4513508670bf724938faad465d2","tid":1942603,"uid":132888,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T07:33:42.000Z","msg":"自推一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6f2c81c064428da311e64e10012fd9be90eaf2a","tid":1942603,"uid":349945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T07:35:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f381ce86662aa09cb390cd3354d92ce273fc82b8","tid":1942603,"uid":29143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T07:36:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"85c89b75be9da5f9a461545e78adfac18851c63c","tid":1942603,"uid":132888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T07:39:21.000Z","msg":"自推兩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ee26028318722d7901e253110bf9fdb45560e13","tid":1942603,"uid":128217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T07:40:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3456e9bc4705a80483045403f57c00ca0ae8f789","tid":1942603,"uid":305408,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T07:40:36.000Z","msg":"唔可以直接標題屌人幫襯間野咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aacaf06df7ec2ccdde3805916d58d89b86b0591","tid":1942603,"uid":256762,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T07:42:52.000Z","msg":"好食自然有人幫襯，難食